## Asset packaging

How assets reach the apps:

- **iOS:** {{Asset catalog (`Assets.xcassets`); managed by iOS
  team; bumped via design migration when assets change}}
- **Android:** {{`res/drawable-*`; managed by Android team; same}}

When tokens or assets change here:
- File an ADR if the change affects shipping behavior
- Open a migration if multiple repos need to adopt
- The sub-repo task spec references this file

